  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/dfb338f35b56d25c2f7ca5b895432a63.poster.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/dfb338f35b56d25c2f7ca5b895432a63.webm?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/dfb338f35b56d25c2f7ca5b895432a63.mp4?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/238e624304bb6760b6e7af550da89a70.avif?t=1761754319\" width=593 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scholar's Mate is an immersive first-person horror <strong>Escape Room</strong> experience that puts you in the shoes of Judith, a young woman who wakes up in the gloomy facilities of a psychiatric hospital.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/8594e48ec86cb2d1fc53281016bd53bc.poster.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/8594e48ec86cb2d1fc53281016bd53bc.webm?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/8594e48ec86cb2d1fc53281016bd53bc.mp4?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must escape from this macabre place by solving mysteries while avoiding capture by Eddie, your sinister hunter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/be98e02714478abaa9b9c170987271e0.avif?t=1761754319\" width=593 height=134 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first person horror <strong>escape room</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and solve the hidden secrets of the hospital to escape.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relentless pursuit by Eddie.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the tension with an original soundtrack and immersive sound effects designed to create an eerie atmosphere.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/a250945643309ff7ca27b672e4459b4d.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/edb0161b9db9f6489684d466613502c3.webp?t=1761754319\" width=616 height=1 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/94b320f724c2c78a2face0fa0d8a6e50.poster.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/94b320f724c2c78a2face0fa0d8a6e50.webm?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/94b320f724c2c78a2face0fa0d8a6e50.mp4?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/edb0161b9db9f6489684d466613502c3.webp?t=1761754319\" width=616 height=1 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/dfb338f35b56d25c2f7ca5b895432a63.poster.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/dfb338f35b56d25c2f7ca5b895432a63.webm?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/dfb338f35b56d25c2f7ca5b895432a63.mp4?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/238e624304bb6760b6e7af550da89a70.avif?t=1761754319\" width=593 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scholar's Mate is an immersive first-person horror <strong>Escape Room</strong> experience that puts you in the shoes of Judith, a young woman who wakes up in the gloomy facilities of a psychiatric hospital.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/8594e48ec86cb2d1fc53281016bd53bc.poster.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/8594e48ec86cb2d1fc53281016bd53bc.webm?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/8594e48ec86cb2d1fc53281016bd53bc.mp4?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must escape from this macabre place by solving mysteries while avoiding capture by Eddie, your sinister hunter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/be98e02714478abaa9b9c170987271e0.avif?t=1761754319\" width=593 height=134 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first person horror <strong>escape room</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and solve the hidden secrets of the hospital to escape.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relentless pursuit by Eddie.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the tension with an original soundtrack and immersive sound effects designed to create an eerie atmosphere.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/a250945643309ff7ca27b672e4459b4d.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=200 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/edb0161b9db9f6489684d466613502c3.webp?t=1761754319\" width=616 height=1 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/94b320f724c2c78a2face0fa0d8a6e50.poster.avif?t=1761754319\" width=600 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/94b320f724c2c78a2face0fa0d8a6e50.webm?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095510/extras/94b320f724c2c78a2face0fa0d8a6e50.mp4?t=1761754319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/